I identified a concrete, low-risk gap to fix: serialized metadata payloads (like `dedupe_signature` JSON strings) are not currently unpacked before frame-feature extraction, so frame terms embedded there can be missed. I’m patching the selector to parse structured JSON-like strings deterministically, and expanding codec metadata harvesting to include citation/top-feature fields directly.
